data.description: THIS HOME HAS THREE FLOORS OF FINISHED LIVING SPACE. IT HAS HARDWOOD FLOORS THROUGH OUT, WINDOWS ARE FROM 2020! THIS HOME FEATURES A NICE SIZE LIVING ROOM THAT FLOWS RIGHT INTO AN ELEGANT DINING ROOM WITH BEAUTIFUL CROWN MOLDINGS THROUGH OUT. THERE IS ANOTHER ROOM THAT CAN BE USED AS AN OFFICE OR PLAYROOM. THE ATTIC IS NOT ONLY SPACIOUS BUT IT FEATURES A BEDROOM AND A 2ND BEDROOM (BEING CURRENTLY USED AS AN OFFICE). THE BASEMENT HAS PLENTY OF SPACE FOR ANOTHER FAMILY ROOM AND A 5TH BEDROOM!!  THIS HOME WONT LAST VERY LONG! VERY MOTIVATED  SELLER! LOW TAXES NO HOMEOWNERS EXEMPTION YET APPLIED. THIS HOME ALSO COMES WITH A ONE YEAR HOME WARRANTY! COME SEE FOR YOURSELF YOU WONT BE DISAPPOINTED!
